  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0db8 \u0dbb\u0dcf\u0da2\u0db4\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dbd\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dda \u0db8\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd9\u0db8\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "I am not a friend of Rajapaksa",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickramasinghe said that he is not a friend of the Rajapaksas but a friend of the people at Hunupitiya Gangarama Temple.",
        "The President said this in response to a question put to him after joining the religious ceremonies at Hunupitiya Gangarama Temple after being elected as the President.",
        "Question - Mr. President, the people say they want change. You are a friend of the Rajapaksa, aren't you? Then how can there be a change?",
        "Answer- How can Rajapaksa become my old friends? I was always against them. You came today and the Rajapaksa's are my friends.",
        "I will say one thing. When you become a journalist, you need to study deeply. Do not ask such questions."
      ],
